Cycle 1: Project Initialization and Scaffolding.

The objective of this cycle is to initialize the `aiascent.dev` project by creating the foundational scaffolding as outlined in the Technical Scaffolding Plan (A3) and Task T-1 of the Universal Task Checklist (A4).

I have generated the core configuration files required for a modern Next.js application utilizing the App Router, TypeScript, and TailwindCSS. This includes:

