2.  **`src/components/home/MissionSection.tsx`:** To ensure the `LampContainer` properly meets the footer without any visual gaps or overlaps, I will remove the negative bottom margin (`-mb-20`). This will allow the `MissionSection` to occupy its full space, and the footer will follow naturally below it.

These changes will create a more polished and immersive final section for the homepage, resolving the specified visual bugs.

