    *   Increase the width of the conic gradient `motion.div` elements from `w-[50rem]` to `w-[80rem]` to widen the light effect.
    *   Increase the height of the conic gradient `motion.div` elements from `h-56` to `h-96` to make the light cone taller and soften its top edge.
    *   Remove the `pb-20` class from the main container to eliminate the bottom padding that creates the background sliver.
2.  **Update `src/components/home/MissionSection.tsx`:**
    *   Remove the `-mb-20` class from the `section` element to align it correctly with the modified `LampContainer` and the footer.
